---
description: Code review workflow with variable capture
argument-hint: <file-or-directory>
---

# Analyze the code
prompt("Review the code in $1 for bugs and issues") -> $issues

# Get improvement suggestions based on issues found
prompt(<<EOF
Based on these issues:
$issues

Suggest specific fixes with code examples.
EOF
) -> $fixes

# Summarize for the developer
prompt("Create a brief summary of the review:\n\nIssues: $issues\n\nFixes: $fixes")
